These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, epic, fantasy
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, jet-ski
1. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | fantasy | epic    |
| Transport     | airplane    | jet-ski       | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, mechanic, coach
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, badminton
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the coach is on the left of the writer##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the mechanic is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | coach | writer | mechanic  |
| Sport   | sailing  | soccer  | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, social-worker, pilot
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, gospel
1. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
2. the project-manager is on the far right##1
3. the social-worker is the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | pilot | social-worker | project-manager |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep        | gospel    | metal        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, dancing, sudoku
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, lizard
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | dancing | woodworking |
| Pet     | dog  | rabbit    | lizard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, documentary, superhero
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | time-travel | superhero |
| Transport     | car   | bus   | quad-bike   |

