2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | fishing | rock-climbing      |
| Job     | teacher  | project-manager | freelancer |

