.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, gospel, country
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, argentine
1. the fan of country is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the argentine is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | country    | classical       |
| Nationality   | indonesian | argentine | american |

