.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, sprite
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, eggplant, blueberry
1. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person eating eggplant is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | sprite        | tea  | lemonade   |
| Food       | blueberry | eggplant | nectarine |

