.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, soy-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, polish, indonesian
1. the dutch is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2
2. the polish is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the dutch is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | cola    | soy-milk    | juice  |
| Nationality   | polish | dutch | indonesian |

