.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, brazilian, polish
3 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, frog
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the polish is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the mouse##2
4. the owner of the mouse is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | polish | brazilian |
| Pet           | chinchilla    | frog    | mouse       |

