2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | photography    | collecting   | cooking |
| Sport   | badminton | climbing | skiing |

