.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, western, sports
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, salsa, punk
1. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
2. the person watching sports movies is between the fan of punk and the fan of funk##2
3. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of punk is the person watching spy movies##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | sports | spy |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | salsa  | punk    |

