.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, coffee
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, romance, horror
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | iced-tea | lemonade         |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | romance  | epic |

 